Package: bayesdag
Title: Fully Bayesian approaches to causal discovery and causal effect estimation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "First",
           family = "Last",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "first.last@example.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: bayesdag implements a bunch of fully Bayesian methodologies for learning 
  the causal structure of a given set of variables in the so-called causally sufficient case. 
  It also provides some functions for causal effect estimation with uncertain DAGs.
